entries.boss_detected: The Empire is dispatching one of their Ace pilots to investigate, stay cautious.
entries.complete: Amazing job out there pilot! Return to base for some well earned rest.
entries.dd_boss_taunt_1: It's been a long time since I had an actual challenge.
entries.dd_boss_taunt_2: Rebel worm, you should have stayed in your hole.
entries.dd_boss_taunt_3: Your first mistake was coming here. Your second mistake is not fleeing. You only get two mistakes.
entries.dd_boss_taunt_4: My skills are superior in every way.
entries.dd_boss_taunt_5: This ship, my skills, I can't be defeated!
entries.found_loc: More Imperial patrols have been spotted in this area, proceed when ready.
entries.level_boss: One of the Empires Ace pilots is attacking; he's piloting one of their experimental fighters. Good luck pilot!
entries.level_boss_dead: I'm impressed! The Empire will speak your name in fear pilot.
entries.level_increase: Our spy ships report that the Empire is increasing their presence in the sector to try and stop our attacks.
entries.quest_destroy_d: We will keep updating your nav computer with new areas of possible targets. Keep going until you have exhausted yourself, your ship or until you feel you have had enough.
entries.targets_behind: Tactical Computer: < Be aware, vessels trying to target this ship with their weapon systems. Attack originating direction 180 degrees. >
entries.targets_detected: Tactical Computer: < Vessels fitting hunted ship profile on attack vector, weapon systems armed. >
entries.taunt_2: You will pay for your crimes!
entries.taunt_3: Your pathetic attacks end here Rebel!
entries.title: Dathomir system: Duty mission: Attack Imperial patrols.
entries.title_d: Hunt down Imperial fighters in the Dathomir System.
